channel.title: A little project me and Davidi2 worked on
channel.description:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dxyV1MzXEEE
Goes from his house to mine and vice versa =D
on a side note at the corner of the z and x intersection I plan on building a tiny train station so we can go other places.
